articles.author: Larry Madowo, Stephanie Halasz
articles.title: South African rapper Costa Titch dies after video surfaces of him collapsing on stage - CNN
articles.description: South African rapper Costa Titch died suddenly this weekend, his family said on Instagram, hours after he performed at a music festival.
articles.content:
